<item>
            <title>[SOLR-174] Add multi-param support to qf,pf,bf,bq</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-174</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A quick patch that adds multi-params support for the listed dismax params.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I opened an issue to get some feedback on the bq situation.  I left the subquery-extraction logic as in, applying it to each specified boost query.  I&apos;m not sure this is still valid given coordFactor and such.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
